{
  "stem": "11075.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Barracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was not, you know-- nobody could live a whole year, because no heat, nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was the food like?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Miserable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us food, you know, that-- that you could-- you could take it out, give it back, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes, on Sunday, they gave us a piece of bread, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A piece-- a piece bread with-- with water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very difficult.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From Sonnenburg--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them, they said, you know, I will not make it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe if I will be dead, maybe it will be much easier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Much easier, so I will forget the whole story, the whole thing, you know, what we have gone through after so many years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After so many years fighting, you know, for the life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because, you know, that was no life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no life, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Matter of fact, that's-- when the-- the Germans came, sometimes you can see in the movie also, in the television, that you know-- that once in a while, they're showing how they-- how they burned the synagogues, and everything.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't have-- and here, if somebody wants to be a religious man, only-- only quiet, you know, that nobody will be able to see and to hear, if somebody is a religious man.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the liquidation, Sonnenburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The liquidation Sonnenburg.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was from a couple thousand, was only one road from east to west, and from both sides was forest that they called the Death March.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In German, the Death March.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same thing, the same-- same uniform, same-- same stripes, you know, with the number and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
